Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\DeliveryOptimization\Settings
and change the SZ string
DownloadMode
to
0

&

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\System\ControlSet001\Services\DoSvc
and change the DWORD string
Start
to
3


Finish. No restart required. You can config this in Windows update settings too.
